working specifically

00:37:44.220 --> 00:37:48.420
on expanding hospital safety and
access, and a lot of their work

00:37:48.420 --> 00:37:50.550
is trans focused.

00:37:50.550 --> 00:37:52.260
At the state level--

00:37:52.260 --> 00:37:54.540
